%% Diagram: Spanner Commit Wait
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Coord as Coordinator
    participant Replica
    participant TT as TrueTime

    Client->>Coord: BEGIN T1
    Coord->>TT: TT.now()
    TT-->>Coord: [earliest, latest], ε≈4ms
    Note over Coord: pick s = latest
    Coord->>Replica: prepare T1 @ s
    Replica-->>Coord: prepared
    Note over Coord: commit-wait until TT.after(s)<br/>≈ 2ε ≈ 7-14ms
    Coord-->>Client: ack T1
    Note right of Coord: Any T2 starting after the ack<br/>sees s(T2) > s(T1).
